@item Generate sparse matrices:
  @dfn{spalloc}, @dfn{spdiags}, @dfn{speye}, @dfn{sprand}, 
  @dfn{sprandn}, @dfn{sprandsym}

@item Sparse matrix conversion:
  @dfn{full}, @dfn{sparse}, @dfn{spconvert}

@item Manipulate sparse matrices
